Package: snd-zg01-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, dkms (>= 2.1.0.0)
Description: DKMS driver for Yamaha ZG01 USB audio interface
 This package provides the snd-zg01 kernel module for the Yamaha ZG01
 USB audio interface (VID: 0x0499, PID: 0x1513).
 .
 Features:
  - Game Channel (Output): Crystal-clear 32-bit stereo playback
  - Voice Channel (Input): Low-latency microphone capture
  - Full-duplex support for simultaneous playback and capture
  - 48kHz sample rate, S32_LE format
  - Perfect audio quality with no clicks or sample skipping
 .
 The module will be automatically rebuilt for new kernel versions
 using DKMS (Dynamic Kernel Module Support).
